title: Quiet Apt available on horse property
posting_body: ['Interview now for Sept 🐴 Small Apt for 1 person - 1 car / strong horse knowledge required ability to help with turn out  feeding occasionally .', 'Quiet gated.', 'Non smoking safe community with lovely yard and walking trails near.by.', 'Easy access to shopping 520 etc', 'but this is county life not for the “city types”.', 'Set up for Comcast/ water- sewer included In rent/ tenant responsible for garbage PSE and heat, Ideal for a work from home situation as this is.', 'Very quiet Upstairs apt/ hardwood floors own kitchen washer dryer covered parking for 1 car only.1 large bedroom/ Tenant below is quiet teacher-', 'another teacher in Redmond area would be a great fit also-', 'No dogs please respect this as we have service dog on site- kitty is ok.', 'Extensive background check will be done for 35.00 tenant applicant pays-References will be checked as well.', 'First last damage.', 'Please contact Ernie property manager 🐴 Thanks']
